cu.explanation_en: Setting the remote SCTP address to an unreachable IP '10.0.0.1' will cause routing failures, preventing the CU from establishing F1 connection to the DU.

du.explanation_en: Setting the downlink absolute frequency point A to 0 (invalid value) will cause frequency misalignment, resulting in downlink carrier setup failure and cell initialization errors.
du.explanation_zh: 將下行鏈路絕對頻率點 A 設定為 0（無效值）會導致頻率錯位，造成下行鏈路載波設定失敗和細胞初始化錯誤。
